            {
               "text": "<span class=\"desc\"><img id=\"bndPortugal6r\" src=\"images/BibliotecaNacionalDigital/BNDTordesillas_6r.jpg\" class=\"imgcenter\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('bndPortugal6r', '0%')\" />Figure 1: Page from the Treaty of Tordesillas (<a href=\"#\" onclick=\"htCleanSources(); htFillPrimarySource('086440f2-0df7-4589-ac73-0353cf1b5312'); return false;\">Biblioteca Nacional de Portugal - BNP, BN MS. 5, n.º 25, F. 6r</a>). <span id=\"bndPortugal\"></span>).</span></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
